#

Vegan Waffles

25 min
$8
200 kcal
Difficulty: 30%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

Gluten

Dietary Tags:

VeganDairy-FreeNut-Free

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Breakfast

Tags:

BreakfastBrunchVeganSweet

Description

Deliciously fluffy vegan waffles that are perfect for breakfast or brunch, topped with your favorite fruits and syrup.

Ingredients

  • all-purpose flour: 1 1/2 cups
  • almond milk: 1 1/4 cups
  • baking powder: 2 tablespoons
  • coconut oil: 3 tablespoons, melted
  • maple syrup: 2 tablespoons
  • vanilla extract: 1 teaspoon
  • salt: 1/2 teaspoon
